			(161, 'You work for a company that uses AWS to store documents. These documents are not accessed very often. However, when a document is requested, it needs to be made available within 20 minutes. Which of the following options would be very cost-effective for this use case?', 'Amazon S3 Intelligent - Tiering', 'Amazon S3 Glacier Instant Retrieval', 'Amazon S3 Glacier Flexible Retrievals', 'Amazon Glacier Deep Archive', '', '', 'C', 'The S3 Glacier Instant Retrieval storage class delivers retrieval in milliseconds S3 Glacier Flexible Retrieval provides three retrieval options: Accelerated retrievals that typically complete in 1-5 minutes, Standard retrievals that are typically ready in 3-5 hours, and Free-Bulk retrievals that retrieve large amounts of data typically in 5-12 hours. The Amazon S3 Glacier Deep Archive storage class provides two retrieval options, ranging from twelve to 48 hours.'), 
